--tooltip-padding-y: 0.25rem;   /* 4px */
--tooltip-radius: 0.25rem;      /* 4px */
--tooltip-font-size: 0.6875rem; /* 11px */
--tooltip-min-width: 60px;
--tooltip-max-width: 240px;     /* ~37-41 chars per line (11px Mona Sans) */
```

**Width rules:**
- Tooltip uses `w-max` with `min-w-[var(--tooltip-min-width)]` and `max-w-[var(--tooltip-max-width)]`
- Short text stays compact; long text wraps at 240px (~37-41 characters per line)
- Do NOT use `whitespace-nowrap` — long tooltips must wrap to avoid overflowing into sidebars or off-screen

