## Popover 사용법

```tsx
// 기본 (클릭 트리거)
<Popover
  trigger="click"
  position="bottom"
  content={
    <div className="p-4">
      <p className="text-body-md text-[var(--color-text-default)]">
        Interactive content here
      </p>
    </div>
  }
>
  <Button variant="secondary">Open Popover</Button>
</Popover>

// 호버 트리거
<Popover
  trigger="hover"
  position="top"
  delay={200}
  hideDelay={150}
  content={<div className="p-3">Hover info</div>}
>
  <Button variant="ghost">Hover me</Button>
</Popover>

// 인터랙티브 콘텐츠 (폼, 메뉴 등)
<Popover
  trigger="click"
  position="bottom"
  content={
    <VStack gap={3} className="p-4 w-[280px]">
      <h4 className="text-heading-h6">Quick Settings</h4>
      <FormField label="Display Name">
        <Input placeholder="Enter name" fullWidth />
      </FormField>
      <HStack gap={2} className="w-full">
        <Button variant="secondary" size="sm" className="flex-1">Cancel</Button>
        <Button variant="primary" size="sm" className="flex-1">Save</Button>
      </HStack>
    </VStack>
  }
>
  <Button variant="primary">Open Form</Button>
</Popover>

// 화살표 없이
<Popover showArrow={false} trigger="click" content={<div className="p-3">No arrow</div>}>
  <Button variant="outline">No Arrow</Button>
</Popover>

// Controlled 상태
const [isOpen, setIsOpen] = useState(false);
<Popover
  trigger="click"
  isOpen={isOpen}
  onOpenChange={setIsOpen}
  content={<div className="p-4">Controlled content</div>}
>
  <Button variant="secondary">Controlled</Button>
</Popover>
```

**Popover vs Tooltip:**
- **Tooltip**: 텍스트만, 비인터랙티브, hover 전용
- **Popover**: 인터랙티브 콘텐츠 (폼, 메뉴, 버튼), click/hover 지원, `aria-haspopup="dialog"`

**Props:**
- `content`: ReactNode - 팝오버 내용
- `position`: `"top" | "bottom" | "left" | "right"` (기본: `"bottom"`)
- `trigger`: `"click" | "hover"` (기본: `"click"`)
- `delay` / `hideDelay`: hover 트리거 시 지연(ms)
- `showArrow`: 화살표 표시 (기본: `true`)
- `isOpen` / `onOpenChange`: Controlled 상태
- `closeOnOutsideClick`: 외부 클릭 닫기 (기본: `true`)
- `closeOnEscape`: ESC 키 닫기 (기본: `true`)
- `disabled`: 비활성화
- `aria-label`: 접근성 라벨

