## FormField Spacing Rules

### Spacing

| 컴포넌트 | 간격 | `spacing` prop |
|---------|------|--------|
| Input/Select/NumberInput | Label ↔ Input: 8px, Input ↔ HelperText: 8px | `default` |
| FormField | Label ↔ Input: 8px, Label ↔ Description: 4px, Description ↔ Input: 8px, Input ↔ HelperText: 8px | `default` |
| Checkbox (단독) | Label ↔ Checkbox: 12px, Label ↔ Description: 4px, Description ↔ Checkbox: 12px | `loose` |
| Radio/CheckboxGroup | Label ↔ Options: 12px, Label ↔ Description: 4px, Description ↔ Options: 12px | `loose` |
| Toggle | Label ↔ Toggle: 12px, Label ↔ Description: 4px, Description ↔ Toggle: 12px | `loose` |

### Typography

| 구분 | 위치 | 스타일 |
|------|------|--------|
| Description | 라벨 하단 | `text-body-md` (12px/18px) |
| HelperText | Input 하단 | `text-body-sm` (11px/16px) |

### `spacing="loose"` 규칙

Checkbox(단독), Radio/CheckboxGroup, Toggle을 `FormField`로 감쌀 때는 **반드시** `spacing="loose"`를 사용합니다.

```tsx
// Checkbox (단독) — spacing="loose" 필수
<FormField label="Favorite" spacing="loose">
  <Checkbox label="Mark as Favorite" checked={isFavorite} onChange={...} />
</FormField>

// Toggle — spacing="loose" 필수
<FormField label="Enable notifications" spacing="loose">
  <Toggle checked={enabled} onChange={...} />
</FormField>
```

